Class Complaint

java.lang.Object
universityProject.dev.academicEntities.Complaint
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Complaint extends Object implements Serializable
Version:
18.12.2023 The Complaint class represents a complaint made within the academic entities of the university. It contains information such as the complaint ID, text, urgency level, sender, and the accused party.
